# Trivy allowlist for known/accepted CVEs (PETPLAT-105).
#
# One CVE ID per line. Only add an entry here after reviewing the scan
# report artifact (uploaded by build-push.yml as "trivy-{service}") and
# confirming the finding is a false positive or genuinely accepted risk —
# never add an entry just to make a failing build pass.
#
# Format:
#   CVE-2024-XXXXX
#
# Example (remove when adding a real entry):
# CVE-2023-00000
